                <h1>How to Change Your Zoom Background: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change your Zoom background, start a meeting and click on the arrow next to the "Stop Video" button. Select "Choose Virtual Background." You can upload your own image or choose from Zoom's default options. Ensure good lighting for best results. Enjoy a fun, professional, or themed background in your meetings!</p>
